<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 20:08:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>关于色情、性工作（甚至 Cicciolina）的以色列诗歌会让你心碎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-poems-on-porn-sex-work-and-even-cicciolina-that-will-break-your-heart/00000190-3150-d700-a7f0-bdf25c170000</link><description>一本关于卖淫、受害者和嫖客的以色列新诗选，为以色列社会提供了罕见且不同的视角</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 18:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-poems-on-porn-sex-work-and-even-cicciolina-that-will-break-your-heart/00000190-3150-d700-a7f0-bdf25c170000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列军队无视观察员关于哈马斯在 10 月 7 日之前在边境附近举行“不寻常”训练的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/idf-ignored-warning-by-army-spotter-that-hamas-held-unusual-training-days-before-oct-7/00000190-36e0-d6fa-abb4-77ef0c840000</link><description>据以色列公共广播公司 Kan 11 报道，观察员报道称，大约 170 名哈马斯特工正在训练如何在攻击以色列坦克兵的同时发射火箭，这一例行程序于四天后（即 10 月 7 日）实施</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 18:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/idf-ignored-warning-by-army-spotter-that-hamas-held-unusual-training-days-before-oct-7/00000190-36e0-d6fa-abb4-77ef0c840000</guid></item><item><title>白宫炮轰攻击拜登的视频“令人失望”，内塔尼亚胡谴责“人身攻击”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-personal-attacks-as-white-house-blasts-disappointing-video/00000190-36ab-de3a-a19a-f6abd2180000</link><description>国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比为拜登政府辩护，反对内塔尼亚胡公开指责其推迟向以色列运送武器。共和党参议员汤姆·科顿也加入了对内塔尼亚胡的攻击，称白宫的行为是“官僚花招”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 18:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-personal-attacks-as-white-house-blasts-disappointing-video/00000190-36ab-de3a-a19a-f6abd2180000</guid></item><item><title>正统派和以色列极端民族主义者之间的婚姻是否开始破裂？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/is-the-marriage-between-haredim-and-israeli-ultranationalists-beginning-to-break-up/00000190-3644-de3a-a19a-f6646ba00000</link><description>三十年前，极端正统的沙斯党加入了支持和平的左翼政府。但随后正统派政党急剧转向政治极右翼，内塔尼亚胡掌权数十年。但现在出现了重大转变的初步迹象</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:48:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/is-the-marriage-between-haredim-and-israeli-ultranationalists-beginning-to-break-up/00000190-3644-de3a-a19a-f6646ba00000</guid></item><item><title>BDS 将贾斯汀·比伯和拉娜·德雷列入黑名单后，“犹太复国主义”作家又成为攻击目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-blacklisting-justin-bieber-and-lana-del-rey-its-zionist-authors-turn/00000190-365b-d700-a7f0-bffb798c0000</link><description>世界各地的作家都被列入了一份名为“你最喜欢的作家是犹太复国主义者吗？”的病毒名单上的黑名单。诸如参加哈达萨读书俱乐部或称哈马斯 10 月 7 日的行为“不可接受”等“罪行”。抵制他们作品的呼吁效果如何？谁受到的伤害最大？</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-blacklisting-justin-bieber-and-lana-del-rey-its-zionist-authors-turn/00000190-365b-d700-a7f0-bffb798c0000</guid></item><item><title>“这不是你在美国看到的”：犹太说唱歌手兼喜剧演员 Kosha Dillz 在以色列反政府抗议中看到了什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-jewish-rapper-comedian-kosha-dillz-saw-at-an-israeli-anti-government-protest/00000190-3590-d8bc-abf7-b7b25d9c0000</link><description>Kosha Dillz（又名 Rami Even-Esh）自 10 月 7 日以来第四次访问以色列，在特拉维夫一家挤满人的俱乐部表演，但在此之前他参加了一场反政府抗议活动。在参加美国支持巴勒斯坦和支持以色列的集会几个月后，他相信自己拥有“很多人没有的观点”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-jewish-rapper-comedian-kosha-dillz-saw-at-an-israeli-anti-government-protest/00000190-3590-d8bc-abf7-b7b25d9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 258 天：官员称，如果巴解组织不统治加沙，内战将爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-258-civil-war-will-erupt-in-gaza-if-plo-doesnt-rule-it-official-says/00000190-367d-d690-a190-f6ff3d700001</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，加沙地带可能只有 50 名活着的以色列人质 ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了约 25 枚火箭 ■ 巴解组织高级官员称，如果巴解组织不控制加沙，内战将在加沙爆发 ■ 以色列对战争造成的伤亡还没有做好准备以色列电力管理公司首席执行官表示，与真主党合作将对其电网造成影响 ■以下是战争进入 258 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 16:55:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-258-civil-war-will-erupt-in-gaza-if-plo-doesnt-rule-it-official-says/00000190-367d-d690-a190-f6ff3d700001</guid></item><item><title>德国以反犹太主义为由将 BDS 指定为“可疑的极端主义组织”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/germany-designates-bds-as-suspected-extremist-group-citing-antisemitism-concerns/00000190-361d-d700-a7f0-bfffd7250000</link><description>该指定允许德国当局监视 BDS 活动人士并在该组织内招募线人。德国引用了 BDS 宪章中的极端主义证据，该宪章呼吁“解放所有阿拉伯土地”，以及它从哈马斯获得的支持</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 16:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/germany-designates-bds-as-suspected-extremist-group-citing-antisemitism-concerns/00000190-361d-d700-a7f0-bfffd7250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察法律顾问：警察不能在抗议活动中没收标语</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-legal-advisor-police-officers-cannot-confiscate-signs-at-protests/00000190-35e6-d8bc-abf7-b7f6848b0000</link><description>这些命令是在警察暴力没收抗议者标有反政府和战争口号的标语后向以色列高等法院提交请愿书后公布的。尽管如此，在没有法律授权的情况下，没收标志的行为仍在继续</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-legal-advisor-police-officers-cannot-confiscate-signs-at-protests/00000190-35e6-d8bc-abf7-b7f6848b0000</guid></item><item><title>面对与真主党迫在眉睫的战争，以色列有六个艰难的选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/facing-a-looming-war-with-hezbollah-israel-has-six-tough-options/00000190-3434-d5f5-a5d6-fdfead7f0000</link><description>以色列正在应对与加沙哈马斯和胆大妄为的伊朗持续交战的前所未有的局势，同时决定如何应对与黎巴嫩真主党不断升级的跨境战斗。它的下一步行动必须以最经过计算和校准的方式完成——没有犯错的余地</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:55:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/facing-a-looming-war-with-hezbollah-israel-has-six-tough-options/00000190-3434-d5f5-a5d6-fdfead7f0000</guid></item><item><title>日本规模较小：以色列为何决定在 2025 年世博会上低调亮相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-decided-to-lower-its-profile-at-expo-2025-in-osaka/00000190-2b43-d39e-a999-7fcf103b0000</link><description>世博会没有在显眼位置建造豪华展馆，而是在边缘选择了一个小得多的替代方案。 “在我看来，最好不要参与，”提交了原始提案之一的建筑师大卫·克纳福 (David Knafo) 说道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:55:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-decided-to-lower-its-profile-at-expo-2025-in-osaka/00000190-2b43-d39e-a999-7fcf103b0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列有两张脸”：他们逃离俄罗斯，却发现以色列有多相似</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-two-faces-they-escaped-russia-only-to-discover-how-similar-israel-is/00000190-2bf9-d39e-a999-7ffffa300000</link><description>乌克兰入侵后，艺术家维罗妮卡和丹尼尔·伯纳德从俄罗斯移居以色列。这里的生活是他们意想不到的一切：“我们正在努力保持理智和批判性思维”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-two-faces-they-escaped-russia-only-to-discover-how-similar-israel-is/00000190-2bf9-d39e-a999-7ffffa300000</guid></item><item><title>投资者是否正在撤离以色列？到目前为止，数字表明没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/are-investors-bailing-out-of-israel-so-far-the-numbers-say-no/00000190-3638-d39e-a999-76fe04a30000</link><description>对以色列持续投资的真正威胁不太可能是 BDS，而是政府的经济管理不善</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:28:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/are-investors-bailing-out-of-israel-so-far-the-numbers-say-no/00000190-3638-d39e-a999-76fe04a30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员警告电网尚未做好与真主党战争的准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-warns-power-grid-not-prepared-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-361c-d1b6-a19d-b7ffa7900000</link><description>“以色列断电 72 小时后，将无法居住，”负责电力系统监管的公司首席执行官表示。以色列电力公司迅速与“不负责任”的言论保持距离</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:11:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-warns-power-grid-not-prepared-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-361c-d1b6-a19d-b7ffa7900000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡助手对以色列第 13 频道新闻的愿景在泄露的谈话中透露</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-associates-vision-for-israels-channel-13-news-revealed-in-leaked-conversation/00000190-35eb-d8bc-abf7-b7fb72d00000</link><description>任命尤利娅·沙马洛夫·贝尔科维奇（Yulia Shamalov-Berkovich）（内塔尼亚胡总理的亲密助手，没有新闻经验）担任以色列第 13 频道首席执行官的决定遭到电视台员工的广泛抗议。她对新闻媒体的愿景首次在这里透露</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:06:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-associates-vision-for-israels-channel-13-news-revealed-in-leaked-conversation/00000190-35eb-d8bc-abf7-b7fb72d00000</guid></item><item><title>据称，定居者房地产公司出售了不属于其的土地。以色列威胁采取法律行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/settler-real-estate-company-allegedly-sold-land-it-doesnt-own-israel-threatens-to-sue/00000190-35c1-d700-a7f0-bde380960000</link><description>以色列西岸政府当局告诉该公司，他们“在未登记在您名下的土地上销售住房单元”，并要求他们停止。该公司表示，这片土地属于约旦的一名巴勒斯坦人，他愿意出售自己拥有的土地</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 14:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/settler-real-estate-company-allegedly-sold-land-it-doesnt-own-israel-threatens-to-sue/00000190-35c1-d700-a7f0-bde380960000</guid></item><item><title>报告：加沙地带仍活着的以色列人质估计只有50人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/report-number-of-israeli-hostages-still-alive-in-gaza-estimated-to-be-as-low-as-50/00000190-35b0-d690-a190-f5b76ff40000</link><description>《华尔街日报》的一项新调查显示，在加沙被扣押的 120 名人质中，估计不到一半还活着，该调查突显了亲人被关押超过 250 天的家庭成员的绝望情绪</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 13:34:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/report-number-of-israeli-hostages-still-alive-in-gaza-estimated-to-be-as-low-as-50/00000190-35b0-d690-a190-f5b76ff40000</guid></item><item><title>“街上没有人认出我。但我因为写的东西而收到了死亡威胁”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-20/ty-article/.highlight/no-one-recognizes-me-on-the-street-but-i-have-gotten-death-threats-for-things-i-wrote/00000190-3564-d6fa-abb4-77ef9e4e0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名作家在以色列面临着作为一名创意人员的高潮和低谷，而一名男孩则在两个国家都有家</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-20/ty-article/.highlight/no-one-recognizes-me-on-the-street-but-i-have-gotten-death-threats-for-things-i-wrote/00000190-3564-d6fa-abb4-77ef9e4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将就国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的逮捕令请求支付 32,000 美元的律师费</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-32-000-in-legal-fees-for-iccs-arrest-warrant-requests-for-israeli-leaders/00000190-34f6-d690-a190-f4f723980000</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官上个月因加沙战争向以色列总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长约阿夫·加兰特提出逮捕令后，以色列将向两名律师支付 12 万谢克尔的律师费</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 10:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-32-000-in-legal-fees-for-iccs-arrest-warrant-requests-for-israeli-leaders/00000190-34f6-d690-a190-f4f723980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长不会代表司法部长任命他选择的最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-will-not-represent-justice-minister-in-his-bid-to-appoint-a-supreme-court-president/00000190-349f-d690-a190-f49f3c050000</link><description>虽然以色列司法改革的设计者试图废除最高法院院长的资历制度，但以色列总检察长认为应该保留这一制度——它保证了法院的独立性，并将政治与任命过程分开</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 09:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/ag-will-not-represent-justice-minister-in-his-bid-to-appoint-a-supreme-court-president/00000190-349f-d690-a190-f49f3c050000</guid></item></channel></rss>